gaitanalyser.data

Class GaitDataReportGeneration

  • java.lang.Object
    • gaitanalyser.data.GaitDataReportGeneration

  • public class GaitDataReportGeneration
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class GaitDataReportGeneration is responsible of the generation of a final report that will include all the images of the graphics in a single document, in order to facilitate the handling of the information generated by the application for the user. The class GaitDataReportGeneration.java will take as input all the .png files generated by the class and will dump them in a file fileName.xdoc. The class GaitDataReportGeneration.java uses the Java library Apache POI for the generation of this file.
